      "content": "maybe it is just their stress, but i can't help but feel like i'm the cause of it. they work so hard, and then they come here just to deal with my sickness and my slowing down. wouldn't it be kinder if i just... stopped? if i just let go so they could have their lives back without the guilt and the constant worry? it feels almost selfish to keep hanging on like this.",
